nodes.text: Dannar's Claim was created as an oasis for the moisture farmers and headquarters for the Settler's Call. Annileen Calwell became the storekeeper and owner after her husband, Dannar Calwell. It housed shops, a bar, and even a fully functional mechanic shop. It was attacked during the Comet Run Day Battle. Annie Calwell left Dannar's Claim after Orrin Gault's "death".
